{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-template-tsx","path":"/tutorials/quarkus-real-world","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Setup</h1>\n<p>Make sure that the maven tooling in your IDE is present and install Quarkus IDE extensions/tooling if appropriate.</p>\n<p>For example the Eclipse IDE offers Quarkus Tools for this in its marketplace:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/95f2f23fc0647c368032acfa2242ea3f/cda19/install-quarkus-tooling.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.32432432432432%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Eclipse marketplace quarkus tooling\"\n        title=\"Eclipse marketplace quarkus tooling\"\n        src=\"/static/95f2f23fc0647c368032acfa2242ea3f/fcda8/install-quarkus-tooling.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/95f2f23fc0647c368032acfa2242ea3f/12f09/install-quarkus-tooling.png 148w,\n/static/95f2f23fc0647c368032acfa2242ea3f/e4a3f/install-quarkus-tooling.png 295w,\n/static/95f2f23fc0647c368032acfa2242ea3f/fcda8/install-quarkus-tooling.png 590w,\n/static/95f2f23fc0647c368032acfa2242ea3f/cda19/install-quarkus-tooling.png 785w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Once the tooling is installed Quarkus Project will appear in the New Project wizard.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5d04d982f8dd9ddbb2ff6e211722b69a/2a50c/quarkus-project-wizard.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.48648648648649%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"New Project Wizard &gt; Quarkus\"\n        title=\"New Project Wizard &gt; Quarkus\"\n        src=\"/static/5d04d982f8dd9ddbb2ff6e211722b69a/fcda8/quarkus-project-wizard.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5d04d982f8dd9ddbb2ff6e211722b69a/12f09/quarkus-project-wizard.png 148w,\n/static/5d04d982f8dd9ddbb2ff6e211722b69a/e4a3f/quarkus-project-wizard.png 295w,\n/static/5d04d982f8dd9ddbb2ff6e211722b69a/fcda8/quarkus-project-wizard.png 590w,\n/static/5d04d982f8dd9ddbb2ff6e211722b69a/efc66/quarkus-project-wizard.png 885w,\n/static/5d04d982f8dd9ddbb2ff6e211722b69a/2a50c/quarkus-project-wizard.png 925w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>On the next page choose Maven and call the project quarkus-warehouse.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4c2bc47c0d306a5e1cb1f3b3d6ef0f71/d8f62/maven-project-wizard.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.37837837837837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"New Project Wizard &gt; Maven + Name\"\n        title=\"New Project Wizard &gt; Maven + Name\"\n        src=\"/static/4c2bc47c0d306a5e1cb1f3b3d6ef0f71/fcda8/maven-project-wizard.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4c2bc47c0d306a5e1cb1f3b3d6ef0f71/12f09/maven-project-wizard.png 148w,\n/static/4c2bc47c0d306a5e1cb1f3b3d6ef0f71/e4a3f/maven-project-wizard.png 295w,\n/static/4c2bc47c0d306a5e1cb1f3b3d6ef0f71/fcda8/maven-project-wizard.png 590w,\n/static/4c2bc47c0d306a5e1cb1f3b3d6ef0f71/d8f62/maven-project-wizard.png 601w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b9130fd76afd792f7621cf5df2ba3243/43142/maven-artifact-wizard.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.43243243243244%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"New Project Wizard &gt; Maven Artifact + rest resource\"\n        title=\"New Project Wizard &gt; Maven Artifact + rest resource\"\n        src=\"/static/b9130fd76afd792f7621cf5df2ba3243/fcda8/maven-artifact-wizard.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b9130fd76afd792f7621cf5df2ba3243/12f09/maven-artifact-wizard.png 148w,\n/static/b9130fd76afd792f7621cf5df2ba3243/e4a3f/maven-artifact-wizard.png 295w,\n/static/b9130fd76afd792f7621cf5df2ba3243/fcda8/maven-artifact-wizard.png 590w,\n/static/b9130fd76afd792f7621cf5df2ba3243/43142/maven-artifact-wizard.png 599w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Then choose the following quarkus extensions and press finish.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/16c7917c08ac984fe5e40b39014deab7/65654/quarkus-extensions-wizard.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 79.05405405405406%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"New Project Wizard &gt; Quarkus extensions\"\n        title=\"New Project Wizard &gt; Quarkus extensions\"\n        src=\"/static/16c7917c08ac984fe5e40b39014deab7/fcda8/quarkus-extensions-wizard.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/16c7917c08ac984fe5e40b39014deab7/12f09/quarkus-extensions-wizard.png 148w,\n/static/16c7917c08ac984fe5e40b39014deab7/e4a3f/quarkus-extensions-wizard.png 295w,\n/static/16c7917c08ac984fe5e40b39014deab7/fcda8/quarkus-extensions-wizard.png 590w,\n/static/16c7917c08ac984fe5e40b39014deab7/65654/quarkus-extensions-wizard.png 872w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Sources</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://quarkus.io/blog/eclipse-got-quarkused/\">https://quarkus.io/blog/eclipse-got-quarkused/</a></li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":1,"frontmatter":{"date":"December 29, 2020","title":"Create a Warehouse application based on reactive Quarkus","author":"Simon Scholz"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["2006812849","2917690675"]}